@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000

### Sign up
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "gm@example.com",
  "password": "hunter2",
  "displayName": "Test GM"
}

### Log in
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "gm@example.com",
  "password": "hunter2"
}

### Check auth — replace TOKEN with the accessToken from the login response above
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Refresh — uses the cookie automatically, no manual token needed
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh

### Log out
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout

### List monsters — first call fetches, subsequent calls are cached
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/srd/monsters
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Get a specific monster's full stat block
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/srd/monsters/goblin
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Get a spell
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/srd/spells/fireball
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### List equipment
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/srd/equipment
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### List classes (for character creation dropdown)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/srd/classes
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN